en-reports-poll-conspiracy-theories-election-denialism-covid-vaccine_n_64b05d9fe4b093f07cada517" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Huffpost</a> )</p><p> • <strong>Robert Kennedy Jr&#39;s racist, antisemitic and xenophobic views go back decades, report says</strong> : Democratic candidate&#39;s recent false claim that Covid could have been &#39;ethnically targeted&#39; is not an aberration but fits long pattern. ( <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/jul/19/robert-kennedy-jr-racist-antisemitic-xenophobic-views" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Guardian</a> ) <em>see also</em> <strong>The Most Shocking Aspect of RFK Jr.&#39;s Anti-Semitism</strong> : What&#39;s surprising isn&#39;t that Kennedy voiced an anti-Jewish conspiracy, but that it took this long. （ <a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/ideas/archive/2023/07/rfk-kennedy-covid-anti-semitism/674727/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">大西洋月刊</a>）</p><p> • <strong>Fans Keep Dying at This Country Music Festival. Their Families Want Answers</strong> : At Faster Horses in Michigan, seven reported deaths have occurred over the fest&#39;s short nine-year history. Survivors of a 2021 tragedy want accountability ( <a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/faster-horses-country-festival-fans-dying-1234783290/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Rolling Stone</a> )<b>  </b></p></blockquote><p>请务必查看本周末我们对 CFA 和特许市场技术员 Jawad Mian <a href="https://ritholtz.com/category/podcast/mib/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-web-url="http://www.bloombergview.com/topics/masters-in-business">的商业硕士</a><a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/masters-in-business/id730188152?mt=2" data-web-url="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/masters-in-business/id730188152?mt=2">采访</a>，他经营着独立的全球宏观研究和交易咨询公司<a class="gtrackexternal" href="https://stray-reflections.com/">Stray Reflections</a> 。该公司专注于主要投资主题，其客户包括许多全球最大的对冲基金和另类资产管理公司。</p><p> <strong>States with weaker gun laws have higher rates of firearm related homici