 Barbie</strong> : The Mattel doll has been through a lot since her 1959 creation—a rise to fame, a public backlash, a breakup, a reconciliation, and much more. Now, though, we&#39;ve entered her latest era—Blockbuster Barbie—which shows that somehow, both the doll and perceptions of her are still evolving. ( <a href="https://www.theringer.com/movies/2023/7/20/23801477/barbie-eras-history-mattel-greta-gerwig-movie" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Ringer</a> )</p></blockquote><p>请务必查看本周末我们对 CFA 和特许市场技术员 Jawad Mian <a href="https://ritholtz.com/category/podcast/mib/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-web-url="http://www.bloombergview.com/topics/masters-in-business">的商业硕士</a><a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/masters-in-business/id730188152?mt=2" data-web-url="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/masters-in-business/id730188152?mt=2">采访</a>，他经营着独立的全球宏观研究和交易咨询公司<a class="gtrackexternal" href="https://stray-reflections.com/">Stray Reflections</a> 。该公司专注于主要投资主题，其客户包括许多全球最大的对冲基金和另类资产管理公司。</p><p> <strong>Americans&#39; Declining Confidence in Institutions</strong><br /> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/shiftinmean.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-316698" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/shiftinmean.png" alt="" width="600" height="425" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/shiftinmean.png 1320w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/shiftinmean-300x212.png 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/shiftinmean-1024x725.png 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/shiftinmean-768x543.png 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/shiftinmean-250x177.png 250w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></a><br /> Source: <a href="https://www.brookings.edu/articles/how-americans-confidence-in-technology-firms-has-dropped-evidence-from-the-second-wave-of-the-american-institutional-con